title: Sign Up (Email)
custom_steps:
WHEN

1. Type email on email field
2. Type password on password field
3. Type same password again to confirm password
custom_expected:
THEN

1. User should be able to type email on email field.
2. User should be able to password on password field.
3. User should be able to type password again on confirm password field.

title: Sign Up (DOB)
custom_preconds:
GIVEN

User wants to register. Select a date using date of birth dropdown menu.
custom_expected:
THEN

1. User should be able to select a month
2. User should be able to select a day
3. User should be able to select a year
